targets.expr:
sum(rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{pod!="" ,namespace=~"temporal|orchestration-workers"}[5m])) by (namespace)
+ on (namespace)
(sum(rate(windows_container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{container_id!="", cluster="$cluster", namespace=~"temporal|orchestration-workers"}[5m]) * on (container_id) group_left (container, pod, namespace) max by (container, container_id, pod, namespace) (kube_pod_container_info{container_id!="", namespace=~"temporal|orchestration-workers"}) OR kube_namespace_created * 0) by (namespace))

sum(container_memory_working_set_bytes{pod!="", namespace=~"temporal|orchestration-workers"}) by (namespace)
+ on (namespace)
(sum(windows_container_memory_usage_commit_bytes{container_id!="" ,namespace=~"temporal|orchestration-workers"} * on (container_id) group_left (container, pod, namespace) max by (container, container_id, pod, namespace) (kube_pod_container_info{container_id!="", namespace=~"temporal|orchestration-workers"}) OR kube_namespace_created * 0) by (namespace))
